://www.ajd-info.fr/html/news.html\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">http://www.ajd-info.fr/html/news.html</span></a></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 35.4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\"><a href=\"http://classe1964.chez.com/MSM%209.html\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">http://classe1964.chez.com/MSM%209.html</span></a></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 35.4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">http://www.SGA.me?moiredeshommes.fichede?tail.webarchive</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 35.4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\"><a href=\"http://pagesperso-orange.fr/cne_legrand/accueil.htm\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">http://pagesperso-orange.fr/cne_legrand/accueil.htm</span></a></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 35.4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\"><a href=\"http://www.lerot.org/FFLSAS/index.php?ind=fflbase&action=showdoc&docno=201\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">http://www.lerot.org/FFLSAS/index.php?ind=fflbase&action=showdoc&docno=201</span></a></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 35.4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Ouvrages:</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span> </span>Remember, les parachutistes de la France libre, Raymond Forgeat, Ed. SHAT 1990.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm -14.5pt 0.0001pt 0cm; text-indent: 35.4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Bérets rouges en Indochine, La ½ Brigade SAS, Raymond Muelle, Presse de la Cité, Ed. 1986.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span> </span>Histoire des parachutistes français, Direction Paul Gaugac, Editions Albatros, </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 35.4pt; text-indent: 35.4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Ed. 1975, volume double 1 & 2.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span> </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">© JF Bianchi 02-2010<span> </span>-<span> </span><a href=\"mailto:jf.bianchi@wanadoo.fr\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">jf.bianchi@wanadoo.fr</span></a></span></p>\n<p> </p>', '2010-08-22 07:01:05', '1566', 'fr', 0);
