(251, 'ADMIN75', 'admin75@fflsas.org', NULL, 'Nichola', 'lewis.nichola@gmail.com', 'Philippe Fauquet/André Zirnfeld', 'Hi,\r\n\r\nI\'m correcting a French to English translation of Marie Chamming\'s \"J\'ai Choisi La Tempête\". In the French text, she says that Fauquet saw André Zirnfeld die (which is possible as they were on the same mission). \r\n\r\nBut Wikipedia says that Zirnfeld\'s jeep had a flat and he was only with François Martin the others in the airfield mission having already already left. Is the Wikipedia version correct?  In the English translation of the Wikipedia entry, the dates are incorrect, which makes me wonder if the rest of the article is accurate. \r\n\r\nMany thanks in advance for your help. This site has already been a huge help for spelling and fact checking! \r\n\r\nBest wishes,\r\nNichola Lewis\r\n\r\n(I\'m English, but live in Brittany)', '2019-10-06 07:45:03', NULL),
